.TH "omap_mcbsp_dma_reg_params" 9 "omap_mcbsp_dma_reg_params" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
omap_mcbsp_dma_reg_params \- returns the address of mcbsp data register
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" omap_mcbsp_dma_reg_params
.BI "(struct omap_mcbsp *mcbsp "  ","
.BI "unsigned int stream "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "mcbsp" 12
omap_mcbsp struct for the McBSP instance
.IP "stream" 12
Stream direction (playback/capture)
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the address of mcbsp data transmit register or data receive register
to be used by DMA for transferring/receiving data
